{"tid":2396512,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[生啤加油] ViuTV收益升22%至3.17億，EBITDA虧損減少40%至1.65億","createTime":"2021-02-05T15:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T12:34:20.000Z","uid":53673,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cf60fe3a035ae56827e383cc99d3529986f55302","tid":2396512,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:47:52.000Z","msg":"ViuTV員工/藝員真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇個勢<br />\n兩年後就開始有錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nVIUTV全年業績：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFKspkN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFKspkN.png&h=f4d1a3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（Source: <a href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2021/0205/2021020500636_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2Fsehk%2F2021%2F0205%2F2021020500636_c.pdf&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjMFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=44d3a98a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2021/0205/2021020500636_c.pdf</a>）"},{"pid":"0c6cb63f22abbfc3286f4341b96460c3732e8b9c","tid":2396512,"uid":53673,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"突登搵埋CCTVB份中期業績嚟笑下<br />\n一個台就淨係用收視打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一個台就可以化做實質收益<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCCTVB：<br />\n「法證先鋒IV」及「機場特警」分別錄得平均收視率36.3點及33.2點，而「殺手」大 結局的收視率更高達35.2點。<span class=\"red\">這些強勁收視率必將為疫情後的廣告業務復甦奠定好基礎</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nVIUTV：<br />\n儘管於疫情期間經濟疲弱及整個市場的廣告開支均有所下降，但受我們電視頻道及數碼平台收視持續上升所推動，<span class=\"red\">ViuTV 的廣告收益增長百分之二十九至港幣 2.71 億元</span>。特別是，選秀節目《全民造星》成為我們的旗艦節目，吸引了眾多廣告客戶及贊助商。"},{"pid":"19609647f0783ac7a9c5fe08b090abcb806be2cb","tid":2396512,"uid":53673,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T16:02:34.000Z","msg":"cap番業績段字出嚟比大家易啲睇：<br />\n<br />\n儘管於疫情期間經濟疲弱及整個市場的廣告開支均有所下降，但受我們電視頻道及數碼平台收視持 續上升所推動，ViuTV 的廣告收益增長百分之二十九至港幣 2.71 億元。特別是，選秀節目《全民造 星》成為我們的旗艦節目，吸引了眾多廣告客戶及贊助商。此外，男團 MIRROR 及 ERROR 通過 《全民造星》系列引起公眾留意並越來越受歡迎，有助我們的藝人管理業務發展。整體收益略為受 到聯合製作收益減少所影響，較去年港幣 2.59 億元增加百分之二十二至港幣 3.17 億元。<br />\n<br />\n由於廣告收益擴大及實施嚴格成本控制措施，截至 2020 年 12 月 31 日止年度，EBITDA 虧損減至港 幣 1.65 億元，較 2019 年大幅改善。<br />\nViuTV 會繼續製作創新且受歡迎的娛樂節目，推動收視上升，並發掘非廣告的商機。"},{"pid":"3dd7978df242351ff3e0d0369bf376df5f073527","tid":2396512,"uid":49853,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"虧損少40%好勁下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b581d25237d14f853ebbbaabf9669f297b94bc","tid":2396512,"uid":27038,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"容我講幾句難聽嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nviu如果之後得返個viu殼<br />\n而內部行政變成cctvb咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我一定會棄之而後快<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望viu可以保持初心，另真心藝人可以有盡情發揮嘅舞台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟一定長睇貴台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54772c8f17f3db1b77cb5263aa9d2125117202f1","tid":2396512,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>容我講幾句難聽嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nviu如果之後得返個viu殼<br />\n而內部行政變成cctvb咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\